data.description: Open House~Saturday 1/27 Noon to 4pm. Welcome to this charming one-story residence! Come inside to see this thoughtfully and sought-after designed one-level home. With no interior steps to navigate, this home is perfect for those seeking a seamless and effortless living experience. This home has been meticulously updated throughout, ensuring modern aesthetics and functionality. You will find ceramic tile consistently throughout the home, along with granite counters and neutral paint colors. Each bedroom has its very own walk-in closet. An additional storage room is available in the attic also. The kitchen is adorned with a strategically placed window over the sink, allowing natural light to flood the space. Culinary enthusiasts will appreciate the breakfast bar, large pantry, and ample granite counters. Plenty of drawers and cabinet space for all your kitchen needs. An oversized living room with built-in shelves and a ton of natural light is perfect for relaxing or family Gatherings. The exterior boasts a traditional and timeless style of four sides of brick and is adorned with professionally trimmed trees. The backyard offers a perfectly manageable size for creating a peaceful oasis for outdoor entertaining.
